@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tiioda(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin(v0) + 0.76)
    v2 = v1
    v2 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.86 / v0 + 0.42) - 0.66))
    v2 = v0
    v2 = ((v1 - (tmp + 0.90 * v0 + 0.25)) - wp.sin((v2 + 0.78 - v2 + 0.59)))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.69) / wp.abs(v2 + 0.38)) / 0.75)
    data[tid] = v0
